   3 &amp; 2 &amp; 1  \cr 

 } } \right]P_k^T$$<br><br>where $$P_k^T$$ denotes the transpose of the matrix P<sub>k</sub>. Then which of the following option is/are correct?

questions.solution:
$${P_1} = I = \left[ {\matrix{
   1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 
